    "village_history": {
      "narrative": "Manjari is a village with multiple communities living together, including Kond and Kunba communities. The village has a rich tradition of collective activities, community rituals, and festivals celebrated together. The village was settled by people who migrated from elsewhere. Traditional Pola festival (Bull worship) is an important annual event celebrating agricultural heritage.",
      "narrative_local": "मांजरी गावात अनेक समाज एकत्र राहतात, ज्यात कॉड समाज आणि कुणबा समाज यांचा समावेश आहे. गावात सामूहिक कार्यक्रम, सण उत्सव एकत्र साजरे केले जातात.",
      "timeline_events": [
